      "title": "Litro Gas prices to drop",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); \u00a0Litro Gas said that the prices of Domestic Cooking Gas cylinders will be reduced from the 5th of August.",
        "Litro Chairman Muditha Peiris told News 1st that over 100,000 LP Gas Cylinders were distributed to the local market on Monday (1).",
        "He said the supply will continue despite inclement weather conditions, adding that the shortage has been eliminated to a greater extent."
      ],
